citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50am on
12/15/2015.
Inspector arrived at the facility at 10:50am and knocked on the door, rang the doorbell, called the phone number
and left a message. The inspector left the facility at 11:20am.
